{{Italic title}}

'''''By the Sun and Stars''''' is an editorial documentation of an epic journey [[Circumnavigation|around the globe]] by [[sailboat]].  It was written via a [[logbook]] by Capt. Wladek Wagner while he traversed the vast oceans of the world.  Published in 1986 by Cody Publications, Inc. ([[Kissimmee, Florida]]).

